HEADWORD: Panoistic
<hw>Pan`o*is"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Pan-</ets>
+ Gr. <?/ an egg.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Producing ova only; --
said of the ovaries of certain insects which do not produce
vitelligenous cells.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

